VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \.rawQuery\s*\(|\.execSQL\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:selectionArgs\s*=|bindString\s*\(|bindLong\s*\(|\?,\s*new\s+String
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects direct SQLite rawQuery or execSQL calls that may construct queries without parameterisation.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for SQLite Raw Query with Potential Injection.
